.opencode/skills/sk-doc/create-feature-catalog/SKILL.md:337:# Each per-feature leaf (detected as the feature_catalog doc type; validates the Validation And Tests table taxonomy)
.opencode/skills/sk-doc/create-feature-catalog/SKILL.md:338:python3 .opencode/skills/sk-doc/shared/scripts/validate_document.py <target-skill>/feature-catalog/<category-name>/feature-name.md
.opencode/skills/sk-doc/create-feature-catalog/SKILL.md:341:The staging scope is mandatory until shipped underscore roots are migrated. Do not run this guard against `.opencode/skills` or another ancestor containing legacy `feature_catalog/` or `manual_testing_playbook/` trees.
.opencode/skills/sk-doc/create-feature-catalog/SKILL.md:343:The validator machine-checks the root-catalog structure and each leaf's Validation And Tests table, but not cross-file link targets or source-anchor accuracy. Manually verify:
.opencode/skills/sk-doc/create-feature-catalog/SKILL.md:346:- Every per-feature file is represented in the root catalog.
.opencode/skills/sk-doc/create-feature-catalog/SKILL.md:347:- Source-file tables reference real, stable paths.
.opencode/skills/sk-doc/create-feature-catalog/SKILL.md:355:- `validate_document.py` checks root-catalog structure and, for per-feature leaves reached by a repo-root path, the Validation And Tests table taxonomy.
.opencode/skills/sk-doc/create-feature-catalog/SKILL.md:365:1. Use `assets/feature-catalog-template.md` for the root catalog scaffold.
.opencode/skills/sk-doc/create-feature-catalog/SKILL.md:366:2. Use `assets/feature-catalog-snippet-template.md` for per-feature files.
.opencode/skills/sk-doc/create-feature-catalog/SKILL.md:367:3. Preserve the canonical root path `feature-catalog/feature-catalog.md`.
.opencode/skills/sk-doc/create-feature-catalog/SKILL.md:368:4. Name category folders with a descriptive kebab-case slug such as `category-name`; let the root catalog index own display order.
.opencode/skills/sk-doc/create-feature-catalog/SKILL.md:373:9. Keep the root catalog inventory-first and navigation-focused.
.opencode/skills/sk-doc/create-feature-catalog/SKILL.md:375:11. Run shared validation on the root catalog and per-feature leaves before delivery.
.opencode/skills/sk-doc/create-feature-catalog/SKILL.md:382:2. Never use a feature catalog as a roadmap unless future-state material is explicitly labeled.
.opencode/skills/sk-doc/create-feature-catalog/SKILL.md:385:5. Never leave per-feature files unlinked from the root catalog.
.opencode/skills/sk-doc/create-feature-catalog/SKILL.md:388:8. Never add numeric prefixes to category folder names; the root catalog index owns display order.
.opencode/skills/sk-doc/create-feature-catalog/SKILL.md:390:10. Never put manual execution scenario matrices in the catalog.
.opencode/skills/sk-doc/create-feature-catalog/SKILL.md:398:2. Source anchors cannot be found for a claimed feature.
.opencode/skills/sk-doc/create-feature-catalog/SKILL.md:399:3. The requested catalog mixes shipped behavior with planned behavior.
