    51	**Field notes:**
    52	- `trigger_phrases` must match the H3 feature heading used in the root `feature-catalog.md` (plus natural language alternates)
    53	- `importance_tier: "important"` is reserved for features that should rank as high-signal in skill-advisor routing — omit for standard entries
